 <PERSON> Strat </PERSON> <PERSON> Douthat </PERSON> is The <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION>' Southeastern regional writer, based in <LOCATION> Atlanta </LOCATION>
