id Afghan troops captured <PERSON> O'Brien </PERSON> on June 8, not June 14 as reported earlier, in <LOCATION> Wardak </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Province </LOCATION> next to <LOCATION> Kabul </LOCATION> He said <PERSON> O'Brien </PERSON> was found in rebel company. Police have yet to charge <PERSON> O'Brien </PERSON>, nor have they allowed <PERSON> Desmond </PERSON> or others to meet him. Afghan authorities say they are awaiting the arrival of a <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> diplomat from <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Delhi </LOCATION> in the case. They said he could not come to <LOCATION> Kabul </LOCATION> on Monday because of air transportation difficulties.
