<HEAD>Texas Has Nine on Death Row Who Were 17 at Time of Crime</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: DELETES 5th graf, `Judith Ann ...,' since Neelley was 18 at
the time of the crime; picks up 6th graf, `Timothy Charles ...' Note that
last lead should have been slugged a 2nd Ld-Writethru.</HEAD>
